Entire structure of the project:
├── data/                      # For storing financial data
├── models/                    # Different optimization models
│   ├── markowitz.py           # MPT implementation
│   ├── monte_carlo.py         # Monte Carlo simulations
│   ├── reinforcement.py       # RL-based optimization
│   └── factor_models.py       # Factor-based models (XGBoost/RF)
├── utils/                     # Utility functions
│   ├── data_loader.py         # Functions to fetch and process data
│   ├── performance.py         # Performance metrics calculation
│   └── visualization.py       # Plotting functions
├── api/                       # FastAPI implementation
│   ├── main.py                # API entry point
│   └── endpoints/             # API endpoints
├── notebooks/                 # Jupyter notebooks for exploration
├── tests/                     # Unit tests
├── requirements.txt           # Project dependencies
├── config.py                  # Configuration settings
└── main.py                    # Main entry point